                     <hi rend="smallCaps">GUILTY</hi> 
                     <hi rend="italic">
of uttering to Mrs. Barham only.</hi>
                  </rs>—<hi rend="italic">
                     <rs id="t18780506-540-punishment-63" type="punishmentDescription">
